, <a href="/web/20180712165248/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0016641&amp;fLockTerm=Fracture+Fixation">Fracture Fixation</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712165248/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0149531&amp;fLockTerm=Fracture+of+pelvis">Fracture of pelvis</a>
